Join the exciting world of software development at ** Sprint as a PHP
developer ** in Brisbane!

** The Role **

As part of our team, you'll have the opportunity to bring client solutions to
life by creating custom applications in Laravel and frontend frameworks like
React/Vue. With your experience in creating RESTful API's and integrating them
across micro-services, you'll help our clients stay ahead of the game. Bonus
points for knowledge of AWS and server maintenance!

** What you'll get in return **

  * Join a team with low BS and a focus on a positive work environment. 
  * Work with onshore development teams and continuously grow with learning and development opportunities 
  * Benefit from employee perks, WFH flexibility, and competitive market rates 

_ Diversity and inclusion are strongly supported at Sprint. People of all
nationalities, gender identities, and cultural backgrounds, including
Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander Peoples, are encouraged to apply. _

